"""Patch UIVisible, and ensure we get a warning when it throws
        an attribute error.
        """
com_patch = MagicMock()
seal(com_patch)
with patch.object(saw_14, '_pwcom', new=com_patch):
    with self.assertLogs(logger=saw_14.log, level='WARN'):
        result = saw_14.UIVisible
self.assertFalse(result)
